1st version

1. update configs from redis at each start
    - coin_pool
    - miner
    - current bind
2. switch configs
3. remove dead node from stats

-----------------------

1. Publish JSON configs
    a. miner config
        name -> JSON
        node index.js -pn name -pm configs/miners/name.json

        {
            apiType: 'ccminer' | 'EWBF' | 'Xgminer' | 'FireIce' | 'Claymore' | 'wrapper',
            fileType: 'binary' | 'tgz'
        }

    b. coin/pool config
        name -> JSON
        node index.js -pn name -pc config/coin_pools/name.json

2. Show online nodes
    a. brief [hostname, coin, GPU#, hashrate, mining coin time, uptime]
        node index.js -l

    b. full [hostname, coin, mining coin time, uptime]
        {GPU#, Name, Temperature, gpu_clocks, mem_clocks, wattage/limit, fan.speed, memory.used/total, hashrate}

        node index.js -f

3. Update own stats
    done automaticaly

4. Switch coins/miners on nodes
    1. local
        - manual
        node index.js -sm miner_name -sc coin_pool_name

        - auto (if not manualy set) by profit calculator

    2. remote all
        node index.js -r all -sm miner_name -sc coin_pool_name

    3. remote by range [n-n|n,n|n-n,n,n-n,n]
        node index.js -r a-b,c,d,f-h -sm miner_name -sc coin_pool_name

    same for automatical: index.js -r all -u

5. auto update